    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You will have to change the new line separator in the file. In linux, there is a utility called <a href=\"http://linuxcommand.org/man_pages/dos2unix1.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">dos2unix</a> that converts the new line separator of an existing file from dos/windows to linux/unix.</p>\n"
